The Managing Director Nigerian Ports Authority, Mohammed Bello-Koko has congratulated Muazu Jaji Sambo and Ademola Adewole Adegoroye on their appointment as Honourable Minister and Minister of State for Transportation respectively. In a message sighted on his social media handle, Bello-Koko said:  “Congratulations to Muazu Jaji Sambo and Ademola Adewole Adegoroye on your appointments by His Excellency President Muhammadu Buhari as the Honourable Minister and Minister of State for Transportation respectively.” The NPA Chief Executive added that, “your wealth of experience and track record of excellent performance will undoubtedly add fillip to on-going efforts at improving efficiency and advancing the frontiers of trade facilitation”. 